Comment: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:02.81,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Love is magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.02,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Attack the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:06.16,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}On Saturday nights at six, click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:08.19,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's Conan's 15th anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.24,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Let's solve the monster movie mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.99,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:13.82,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:16.29,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:57.40,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:57.46,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:57.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:01:57.54,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:57.58,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:57.62,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:57.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:03.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,The Giant Monster "Gomera" Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the real Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mikami-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the ones who wanted to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:41.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Director Mikami-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Nmy friend and creator of Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:44.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Movie Director\NDaisuke Mikami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,Nice to meet ya, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:49.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, would you like to\Nsee Gomera close up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:50.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's break time for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These buildings are tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera's back is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:12.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A person was born from Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a suit.\NThey film it to make it look like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:20.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the monster is rampaging\Nthroughout this miniature city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These buildings sure are well-made...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your filthy hands off, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:29.28,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Artist\NRyōta Adachi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:29.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wreck the set and you'll pay dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director! Do something\Nabout these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:40.66,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera Actor\NShūgo Matsui
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to watch them for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any scenes until this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it, Matsui-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera is on kids' sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:51.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera always rampages because\Nof bad adults, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:57.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Actress\NTomomi Sakaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:58.35,Dialogue,,0001,0001,0020,,And it's Emera the fairy who quiets Gomera's rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:03.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Emera? The ring fairy who comes\Nout only when there's trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! Emera's this tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't she a little old?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hush, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:17.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice staff you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They all love Gomera,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're like a family that's\Nworked with Gomera for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:27.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That will end this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:31.55,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Movie Producer\NOsamu Kamei
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0020,,Monster movies are childish. Their time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Worn-out music\Nand tedious direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over-expensive sets\Nand special effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fairy that was 14 when\Nshe debuted is now 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. I hear yesterday's\Nrush film is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go watch it in the screening room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:05:00.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Say, want to grab a bite, Tomomi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?\NThere's still the matter to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What matter to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about his next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to be the leading\Nrole as a policewoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:16.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he blame people and\Nthen ask something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's to complain about?\NAt least you got some work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're left out in the cold.\NRight, Macchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:28.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he asked me\Nto be the villain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:35.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Let's go check\Nout the majestic Gomera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Matsui-{\i1}kun{\i0}.\NThe kids are all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:37.50,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:37.54,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.41,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Storeroom #1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! There's so many monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:45.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the ones that Gomera beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I didn't think\Nyou'd be that scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gomera's hand.\NWe use it in close-up shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a remote-controlled face.\NWanna see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec while I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:13.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Gomera movies really\Ngoing to end? They're so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He did say they cost lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the food costs!\NGomera {\i1}is{\i0} big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What a bunch of simpletons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your leg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:36.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in here! And he\Nstabbed me with a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran out that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he that producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsui-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's no good, he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Footprints? He must've escaped through that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Gomera?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there. I just ran into him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Was that Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! There's no\Nplace to hide up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he flew off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}... Gomera can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:06.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! A suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:15.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's empty! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:21.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Pardon my asking, but where\Nwere you at around 11:30 a.m.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the 1st floor of the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,doing the final\Ncontinuity checks alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So no one can vouch for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:29.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I tend to sweat quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:39.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you entered this storeroom,\Nthe killer was in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:42.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,already in the Gomera costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:52.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave him emergency treatment,\Nbut he needs to get to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have killed\Nhim with that leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the incident occurred,\Nwhy where you here, Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:05.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Producer Kamei to see\Nthe rush of the final Gomera movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really well done, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:12.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unedited film that was just recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To think something\Nlike this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:21.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tomomi-{\i1}san{\i0}. You saw the back\Nof the person in the suit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:25.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I'm not sure who it\Nwas. But the way they ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They had a hard time running.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like they weren't used to wearing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course. That would be the case\Nfor everyone but Matsui-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:40.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}, Sakaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} and Mikami-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than you three, everybody was in the screening room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I watched the rush too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the only one that left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there was\Nanother who snuck out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't know\Nhow this paint got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I snuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed something on the\Nset when I saw the rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:10.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi-{\i1}san{\i0} only snuck\Nout for 4 or 5 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:17.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Four to five minutes? That's not enough time to don the suit, kill someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:21.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and return to the screening room after running up the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:26.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who put this paint here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:35.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember? You left\Nit after the morning rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:41.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why didn't\NMatsui-{\i1}san{\i0} watch the rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:49.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me. All he said was\Nthat he didn't wanna watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:55.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. He's one of\Nthe ones who wanted to quit Gomera...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0} was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:01.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I hear he often\Nvented to the producer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,about being sick of Gomera and\Nwanting to do normal roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:12.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I don't get it. Where could the killer have disappeared to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.73,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We followed the footsteps around\Nthe corner and up the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.\NLet's make a grave for Gomera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then through that\Ndoor to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:25.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Come on, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! His grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! This ain't the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be getting mad like Gomera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Gomera?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! There's no\Ntail mark on the steps!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's proof that Gomera\Nwent up the steps angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:43.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because his tail sticks\Nup when he gets mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hold on! Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:58.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All right! I figured out the trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:08.92,Studio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Studio A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you let us in the studio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no place for kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:20.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes, there's one here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:21.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:31.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:37.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to take\NMatsui-{\i1}kun{\i0} to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:45.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he won't be able\Nto play Gomera with that leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget Gomera, he can't\Neven play a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Have you solved the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I still don't know who did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:01.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did the killer attack\NMatsui-{\i1}san{\i0} in this storeroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:07.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the killer came to get the knife\Nbut was spotted by Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Movie props can't kill people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:20.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait a minute! In that case,\Nonly one person can be the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:31.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. We're going to take\NMatsui-{\i1}kun{\i0} to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:35.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible\Nis in this very room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:45.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Just move your\Nlips to what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on! Let me\Nhave some glory too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Agasa-{\i1}san{\i0}. If you know\Nwho did it, then please explain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how the killer\Ndisappeared from the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Special effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know those holographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:06.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the killer was one\Nof them the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I ran into the killer in\Nthe hall, and even saw them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:16.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, forget what I said!\NThe truth is-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An extremely simple one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:24.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-{\i1}san{\i0} and the children\Nonly saw the killer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:26.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until he or she turned the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:30.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling if the killer\Nwent up the stairs or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there were footprints\Non the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:35.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Follow my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:38.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer placed the footprints\Non the stairs in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly anyone goes onto the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:53.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be strange for\Neveryone to overlook that stairway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:58.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gomera's legs were probably the\Nonly parts used to make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of this, there is a tail mark\Nin the hall but not on the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:08.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer quickly removed the\Nsuit in front of the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:12.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,went down in the opposite\Ndirection, entered a room,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:16.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,lit the suit on fire, and\Ndropped it to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:23.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But would they be able to\Nmake the footprints in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:29.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without knowing the color the\Npaint on the set would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Adachi-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:34.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I just happened to put that\Npaint there before the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:38.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, that doesn't hold up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:41.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:47.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Tomomi-{\i1}san{\i0} and Adachi-{\i1}san{\i0}\Nare lying to cover for the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That paint was placed\Nthere by the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...to use for the footprint trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:16:00.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So these two know who the killer is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:04.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi-{\i1}san{\i0} probably only\Nfollowed Tomomi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s lead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but she should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably saw the killer when\Nshe bumped into him in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So who exactly {\i1}is{\i0} the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:17.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer was among the four\Nwho weren't in the screening room
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:23.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or who left the screening\Nroom at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi-{\i1}san{\i0} was only gone for\N4 or 5 minutes. Not enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:31.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-{\i1}san{\i0} saw the killer with\Nthe children; she's innocent too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That leaves Director\NMikami and Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:37.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0} is seriously injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:41.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Mikami-{\i1}kun{\i0} is my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore this comes as a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:45.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The killer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bothering me! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bothering you? Shoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:58.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just a noisy fly! Shoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:06.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is you, Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:13.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real! He couldn't escape\Nin that suit with his injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:17.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming he really acquired\Nthat injury before the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying his injury was-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. After the murder,\Nhe dropped the suit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:27.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,returned to the storeroom, and stabbed\Nhimself with another knife
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:34.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the children saw his\Ninjury before the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably fake blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This {\i1}is{\i0} a movie set;\Nit would be easy to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:46.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But after they saw his injury, they\Nfollowed Gomera out to the studio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:50.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to the\Nstudio from the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:53.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly did Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0}\Npass ahead of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:18:03.86,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder Scene - Studio
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The studio is right next\Nto the hallway door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:03.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably entered\Nonce the children left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:08.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He then donned the suit and\Nmurdered Producer Kamei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:13.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This trick would need witnesses\Nto follow the paint footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:19.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he chose these children\Nwho couldn't follow as quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are bundles of curiosity;\Ntell them not to go and they'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:29.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The suit was lit on fire to\Ndestroy sweat traces inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What proof is there\Nthat Matsui-{\i1}san{\i0} did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:38.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife he used to stab himself\Nis in the storeroom prop box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably the\Nonly place to hide it;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:44.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he couldn't walk\Nafter stabbing his leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:48.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing-\Nthe shirt he's wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:55.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer ran off at full\Nspeed with the suit still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shirt would naturally\Nbe soaked with sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But his shirt has no sweat stains...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\NBecause he changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He changed it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid can prove this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:19.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}\Nspilled juice on your shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:22.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's weird.\NThere's no stain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you change clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't move\Nwith your stabbed leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not\Nmistaken, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the juice was spilled\Non the floor instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure?\NTry hard to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Little boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Tomomi-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:50.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. I was really sweaty,\Nso I changed shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:53.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shirt is inside my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Check it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you kill Producer Kamei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he give you work\Nin his next movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That had never entered my mind;\NGomera was all I thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:12.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But weren't you the one who\Nwanted to quit Gomera the most?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:16.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something that\NProducer Kamei made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange how everyone\Nencouraged me with sad smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:26.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I only learned of\Nhis lies two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:30.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hastily negotiated with him, but\Nhe said there was no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:36.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as he had already announced\Nthis was the final Gomera movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:43.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone'll have long forgotten\Nthat rubber freak in a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you talk with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:52.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too hard after seeing\Neveryone working hard one last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:58.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I regret nothing. Now Gomera\Nwon't have a final death scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:03.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only feel bad about making\Nthe children see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:11.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Tomomi-{\i1}chan{\i0}. Did you really\Nsee him in the suit from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't see anything.\NHe disappeared so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell by his movements,\Nwithout having to see inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's been my partner\Nfor these past 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6}Two months later, Gomera\Nmade it onto theater screens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The last scene was connected\Nwith all the previous films
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and Gomera's death scene was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:08.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Gomera can now live\Nforever on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:14.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Crowds hold their breaths as they\Nwatch the powerful visuals and plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:19.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yet, Gomera's war cry sounded\Nespecially forlorn to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:23.40,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}as it echoed throughout the theater...
